column2: SELECT     LTRIM(STR(mjd_r,#,#)) AS MJD,     dbo.fSDSS(p.objId) AS ID,     modelMag_g, modelMagErr_g,     modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r,     modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i, p.ra, p.dec  INTO #list FROM detectionindex d      JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON d.objid=p.objid     JOIN Field f ON p.fieldid=f.fieldid WHERE d.thingid=# ORDER BY # GO    SELECT a.*, b.*  FROM #list a CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(a.ra, a.dec, #) b
